    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You have decided that that some weapons are just better than others and you know which ones you enjoy.</p><p> Begining at 3rd level you gain proficiency in hammers and you carry a stack of nails with you at all times.</p><p> This nails are identical to kunai except when you would throw them you can choose to instead hit them with your hammer to launch them at your opponent.</p><p> Once per turn, when you hit a creature with your hammer or nail you can force them to make a Constitution saving throw or inflict the bleeding condition.</p><p></p>",
